QueryCallback.name: ValidateCourtPolicyEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: NAME like ? and AGENCY_ID = ? AND COURTPOLICY_ID != ?

QueryCallback.name: ValidateDepartmentPolicyEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: NAME like ? and AGENCY_ID = ? AND AGENCYPOLICY_ID != ?

QueryCallback.name: GetDetailDictionaryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: VARELEMENTTYPE_ID in (select VARELEMENTTYPE_ID from JIMS2.CSVARELAGENCY where AGENCY_ID = ?)

QueryCallback.name: GetDetailDictionaryReferenceVariablesEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: VARELEMENTTYPE_ID in (select VARELEMENTTYPE_ID FROM JIMS2.CSVARELAGENCY WHERE AGENCY_ID = ? AND ISREFERENCE=1)

QueryCallback.name: AssociationQueryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: VARELEMENT_ID = CAST(? AS INTEGER) AND COURTSUPOPTION_ID = CAST(? AS INTEGER)

QueryCallback.name: AssociationQueryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: COURT_ID = ? AND AGENCYPOLICY_ID = CAST (? AS INTEGER)

QueryCallback.name: GetByCourtAndOidEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: COURT_ID like ? AND AGENCYPOLICY_ID CAST (? AS INTEGER)

QueryCallback.name: ValidateSupervisionConditionEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: NAME like ? AND AGENCY_ID = ? AND CONDITION_ID != CAST (? AS INTEGER)

QueryCallback.name: AssociationQueryEvent
QueryCallback.whereClause: CONDITION_ID = CAST (? AS INTEGER) AND COURTPOLICY_ID = CAST (? AS INTEGER)
